Package: ctschooldata
Title: Fetch and Process Connecticut School Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Al", "Martin", , "almartin@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Downloads and processes school data from the Connecticut State
    Department of Education (CSDE). Provides functions for fetching enrollment
    data from EdSight and historical archives, transforming it into tidy format
    for analysis. Supports data from 2007-2025 via EdSight and the CT Open Data
    portal.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Depends:
    R (>= 4.0)
Imports:
    dplyr,
    readr,
    purrr,
    httr,
    jsonlite,
    rappdirs
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    readxl,
    ggplot2,
    scales
Config/testthat/edition: 3
URL: https://github.com/almartin82/ctschooldata
BugReports: https://github.com/almartin82/ctschooldata/issues
